# Route Map

URL → page/handler map. For frontend file-based routers, this is generated from the routes/pages directory; for code-based routers (e.g. react-router-dom), from the router config; for backends, from route registration files.

## Ownership

This doc owns the **table** of current routes only. Procedure (how to add a route, auth guards, layouts, nav idioms) lives in `patterns/routing.md`. Do not duplicate procedural prose here — link to it.

